dc_description_s: This data layer represents addresses for Waushara County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, NWaushara_Addresses_2018.gdbN. [This data set was developed initially automated by the WI Department of Natural Resources. It is updated and on an on-going basis, by Waushara County. The data contained in this file only covers points address information managed by the County.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
